  "body": "**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Send a message that contains at least 2 rows\r\n2. Tap on the message -> Tap 'edit message'\r\n3. Try to edit different rows\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nThe edit textbox is jumping after trying to tap on the particular row to edit it\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/207578821-28d34e47-d140-4ba2-a9b1-f5156198a5a7.mp4\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nThe edit textbox is tappable and the cursor easily appears on the location where the user tap\r\n\r\n**ENV:** Samsung Galaxy S20+ v10, Huawei p20 light\r\n\r\n**Additional info:**\r\nReproducible in 20% of cases. If it is not reproduced at first, then do the following steps:\r\n1. Go back to the chat list\r\n2. Open chat again\r\n3. Repeat the steps described in the 'steps to reproduce' section\r\n",
